===Noun===
'''decimalisation''' (''uncountable'')
# Conversion to a [[decimal system]].
# Specifically, conversion of the currency of the [[United Kingdom]] in 1971 from [[pound]]s, [[shilling]]s and [[pence]] to a decimal system in which one pound was worth 100 [[new pence]] (later renamed simply ''pence'').

